The Lighter Side
As an alternative to Pan Am's superb and elaborate
First Class Menu, we now offer "The Lighter Side."
Elegantly presented, this swiftly served selection of chilled
gourmet dishes may be requested at any time, allowing
the First Class traveller to eat or sleep when he chooses.

Roast au Vol
Tenderloin of beef roasted on board and carved
to order. Served with an assortment of sauces,
parisienne potatoes and old country vegetable

Lamb Chops "Fleur de Thyme"
French cut lamb chops seasoned with a touch of
thyme and broiled to perfection. Complemented
by sautéed mushrooms, vegetable medley and
parisienne potatoes
Scallopini of Capon "Parma"
Golden brown breast of capon garnished with
tomatoes concassées and mozzarella cheese.
Served with parisienne potatoes and batonettes
